OL,3,CAngela Rayner 'enticing' Cornwall to
OL,4,Caccept elected mayor
OL,6,FAngela Rayner tells ITV West Country
OL,7,Fshe is 'enticing' Cornwall to accept
OL,8,Fan elected mayor
OL,10,FAngela Rayner has told ITV West
OL,11,FCountry she's "not forcing" Cornwall
OL,12,Fto accept an elected mayor but is
OL,13,F"enticing them", as divisions grow
OL,14,Fover the issue between Cornish MPs and
OL,15,Fthe Labour government.
