OL,3,CAngela Rayner 'enticing' Cornwall to
OL,4,Caccept elected mayor
OL,6,FThe deputy prime minister said "people
OL,7,Fwith skin in the game" can have
OL,8,Fincreased powers over things like
OL,9,Ftransport and education, which would
OL,10,Fin turn give them greater economic and
OL,11,Femployment opportunities.
OL,13,FThere is currently only one mayor in
OL,14,Fthe South West and Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,15,Fgovernment is keen to increase that
OL,16,Fnumber in a bid to push power out of
OL,17,FWestminster and into local areas.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
