OL,3,CAngela Rayner 'enticing' Cornwall to
OL,4,Caccept elected mayor
OL,6,FBut the Labour MP for Camborne and
OL,7,FRedruth, Perran Moon, has said in
OL,8,Fresponse: "I can only speak on behalf
OL,9,Fof Camborne, Redruth and Hayle, and
OL,10,Fthe overwhelming feedback I get is
OL,11,Fthat Cornwall will not accept a Mayor."
OL,13,FLast year, Cornwall Council had to
OL,14,Fabandon plans to pursue a level three
OL,15,Fdevolution deal that included an
OL,16,Felected mayor because of significant
OL,17,Fpublic opposition.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
