OL,3,CAngela Rayner 'enticing' Cornwall to
OL,4,Caccept elected mayor
OL,6,FOf more than 6,000 responses to a
OL,7,Fconsultation, 69% of people were
OL,8,Fopposed to having one and just 25%
OL,9,Fwere in favour.
OL,11,F"It would be completely inappropriate,
OL,12,Fin my view, for an area covered by
OL,13,FNational Minority Status to have to
OL,14,Ftake on an English combined authority-
OL,15,Fstyle Mayor, in order to access the
OL,16,Fhighest level of devolution," added
OL,17,FPerran Moon.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
