OL,3,CAngela Rayner 'enticing' Cornwall to
OL,4,Caccept elected mayor
OL,6,F"No other part of the UK covered by
OL,7,FNational Minority Status has to take
OL,8,Fon a Mayor, so why should Cornwall be
OL,9,Fthe exception? It makes no sense when
OL,10,Fwe have a unitary council.
OL,12,F"We should be considering other, more
OL,13,Fappropriate models of governance for
OL,14,FCornwall, such as an Assembly which
OL,15,Fcould be created by adapting the
OL,16,Fcurrent unitary council."
OL,18,FCouncils across England had until the
OL,19,Fend of September this year to respond
OL,20,Fto a government call for devolution
OL,21,Fproposals from local councils.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
