OL,3,CAngela Rayner 'enticing' Cornwall to
OL,4,Caccept elected mayor
OL,6,FDorset, Somerset and Wiltshire have
OL,7,Fsubmitted joint plans for a mayoral
OL,8,Fcombined authority in the region,
OL,9,Fwhile Devon and Torbay's proposal to
OL,10,Fcreate a combined county authority was
OL,11,Fbacked by Labour in September.
OL,13,FThe Labour government could encourage
OL,14,Fa devolution deal for Devon and
OL,15,FCornwall, which it would argue would
OL,16,Fbring greater investment and power.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
